    <item>
      <title>沙特首都将削减人口目标作为城市审查战略</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/saudi-capital-to-cut-population-goal-as-city-reviews-strategy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[沙特阿拉伯首都将推迟到 2030 年将人口增加一倍的目标，因为它正在重新配置旨在支持王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼数万亿美元的沙特经济多元化议程的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/saudi-capital-to-cut-population-goal-as-city-reviews-strategy</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 11:29:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
